creator: Soletechs
descriptionHtml:
Empowers your organization to mobilize your business processes with two goals: less paper use and saving the environment.

The Dynamics ESS (Employee self-services) mobile app is a unique solution on top of Microsoft dynamics 365 and Dynamics AX 2012.

The Dynamics ESS (Employee self-services) mobile app includes the following:
- You can view all your personnel information, benefits, Job details, Identifications, Bank account, and your dependent information.
- You can view, edit, submit, approve over 17 self-services processes such as (Leave request, Leave planning, Leave encashment, Leave return, Ticket request, Ticket encashment, Excuse request, overtime request, loan request, Advance annual, benefit payment, General request, Letter request, End of service notice request, Business trip planning, Business trip payment request, Training planning request, Training payment request, etc.
- You can view monthly payslip details, Daily attendance for you and your team, Loaned items for you and your team, your annual leaves balances, and EOS balances up to date
descriptionShort: empowers organizations to mobilize work to decrease paper using&save environment
